## Quick Answers

### Is this only for landing pages?

No. It works for any conversion-focused page: product pages, checkout flows, signup forms, app download pages.

### Does this run real experiments?

No. It generates hypotheses and plans. You still need an experimentation tool or analytics workflow to validate changes.

### What does the skill file do?

It acts as a reusable instruction layer that shapes how the model approaches conversion audits, friction mapping, impact stacking, copy rewrites, and experiment design.
